ndowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"謝謝。\n現在開始要更加提升技術去面對才行","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"G.B.T.還會繼續下去……\n下次也一定要贏","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"哦哦，很有幹勁耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"因為我已經決定好一定要獲勝","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"絕對要獲勝啊。\n你對G.B.T.是有什麼特別的想法嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"該說是想法嗎……就是有很多……在思考的事情。\n但我自己也還沒，把思緒全部統整好就是了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"但總之，現在，想全力地\n去面對眼前的事","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"嗯嗯。雖然只是稍微聊了一下，\n就已經能從小蘭身上感受到氣勢囉","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"而且，我想在面對G.B.T.的過程中，\n小蘭你現在正在想的事情的答案，\n搞不好也會自然地浮現吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"會……是這樣的嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"嗯！　煩惱的事情或是思考中的事情啊，\n總是會令人不自禁一直去想而導致幾乎要停下腳步","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"但比起停下腳步，為了某件事去行動的時候，\n也許反而更容易砰地一下就看到答案了喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev229-me3-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……是這樣啊。\n那麼為此，G.B.T.也得好好努力才行了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"character